posting_body: ['Charming duplex in the heart of Tremont!', 'Located close to Lincoln Park, many great restaurants and a fast commute to Downtown Cleveland.', 'Easy access to Ohio City, the West Side Market, W.25th, the Detroit Shoreway and Lake Erie.', 'WATER/SEWER INCLUDED.', 'Property Highlights:', '- Hardwood Flooring', '- Living Room & Dining Room', '- Refrigerator & Stove Included', '- Front & Rear Porch', '- Shared Washer & Dryer', '- Basement and Garage Storage', '- Fenced-In Small Backyard w/ Fire Pit', '- Dogs and cats allowed ($25 per pet/per month extra) NO additional pet deposit', '- OFF-street parking', '- Section 8 ok', '- Applicants are subject to background check and income verification', 'UNIT FEATURES', 'Fenced yard, Hardwood floors, Laundry room / hookups, Oven / range, Pet Friendly, Refrigerator', 'Contact Call Or Text me::', 'show contact info']
